l:dependency.name: Jenkins Performance Publisher plugin
l:dependency.l:description: The PerfPublisher plug-in scans for xml tests reports defined in the administration panel and generates trend graphs, computes stats and underline regressions and modifications. The xml files must be generated by your own testing tool.

l:dependency.name: jxl
l:dependency.l:description: JExcelApi is a java library which provides the ability to read, write, and modify Microsoft Excel spreadsheets.
